    <item>
      <title>新西兰将“黄金签证”更改为吸引富裕的移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/new-zealand-changes-golden-visa-to-lure-wealthy-migrants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰正在简化其所谓的“黄金签证”计划，包括删除英语要求，以吸引富裕的移民并帮助激发经济复苏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-09/new-zealand-changes-golden-visa-to-lure-wealthy-migrants</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 09 Feb 2025 01:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
